                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.672/539b: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the High
                        Commissioner in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bristol</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-01-18T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 18, 1927—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>9. The treaty failed of approval by the Senate, the vote being 50 for and 34
                    against.</p>
                <p>Be prepared to proceed to Angora immediately upon receipt of complete
                    instructions which are being telegraphed to you separately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
